title: [Old Ta'Faendryl, River Edge]
description: The end of the road crumbles into a swiftly moving river.  The churning water gleams dimly, rippled rapids appearing black and oily under the night stars.
The end of the road crumbles into a swiftly moving river.  The water churns and grumbles around the foundations of the ancient ruins of homes that once graced its edge.
